DCI gap (train - test): 0.0034

--- Random Baseline (Test) ---
random_0.05: DCI=0.5187 cos_sim=0.8622
random_0.1:  DCI=0.5965 cos_sim=0.6737
random_0.3:  DCI=0.7197 cos_sim=0.2810  (best random)
random_0.5:  DCI=0.6921 cos_sim=0.1761

CBDP (0.6887) vs Random Best (0.7197): Δ=-4.3%

--- Ablation (Test, fresh init 10 epochs) ---
full:     DCI=0.6772 cos_sim=0.3677
λ_div=0:  DCI=0.6218 cos_sim=0.5781  (-8.2% from full)
λ_pla=0:  DCI=0.7128 cos_sim=0.2837  (+5.3% from full)
λ_nov=0:  DCI=0.6810 cos_sim=0.3740  (+0.6% from full)

Key finding: Divergence loss is critical (removal drops DCI 8.2%).
Plausibility loss is counterproductive in embedding space
(removal improves DCI 5.3% to 0.7128, matching random baseline).

Results saved to phase3_results.json
